	measure 'cMOM UP Recipients growth%' = ```
			
			VAR up_arrow = UNICHAR(129137) 
			VAR down_arrow = UNICHAR(129139) 
			VAR current_Recipients = [UP Total Recipients] 
			VAR PP_Recipients = [PPUP Recipients]
			VAR Growth = DIVIDE(current_Recipients - PP_Recipients,PP_Recipients)
			
			RETURN 
			    IF(
			        Growth<0, ROUND(Growth*100,1)&"% "& down_arrow,
			        ROUND(Growth*100,1)&"% "& up_arrow
			    )
			```
		displayFolder: Unique Profiles
		lineageTag: c449d8a5-9289-4480-a9a7-577806997a5e

